I visited to use the T-Mobile Tuesday deal (not set to expire for another 6 days) plus purchased additional items. When I arrived at the drive-thru, Aisha the “manager in training” and Chelsea the drive-thru cashier refused to fulfill my order.  They claimed that T-Mobile Tuesday is only valid on Tuesday at their store, and that honoring my processed order would be like giving “free food away” . This deal is good for the next week, and processed in my paid order! At that point I asked to speak with the manager, and Aisha informed me the manager was not there and I could call the store to speak with someone. I was in front of her and called the store 3 times and received no answer, and then she asked me to leave and come back at 4 pm to fulfill my order that was paid for.  I asked for a refund and was refused to get my money back “because I paid the app and not the store” . When I insisted on a refund Aisha and Chelsea threatened to call the POLICE on me! I was not yelling or anything and was threatened with the police during a crucial time when that can mean life or death.  I have worked in customer service, and this was by far my worst visit to any establishment that I have experienced. I plan to circulate this review because no customer should ever experience such horrendous service, no food and no refund!!!
